          "treatment": "CT abdomen to exclude obstruction. Correct K+/Mg+/PO4. Consider prokinetics (Metoclopramide 10 mg TDS, Erythromycin 200 mg IV TDS). Switch to epidural analgesia. TPN if oral intake not anticipated for > 7 days."
        }
      ]
    },

